title: TV5Monde Secrets d Histoire La Grande-Duchesse Charlotte de Luxe
description:
La Grande-Duchesse Charlotte de Luxembourg

History Documentary hosted by Stephane Bern, published by TV5Monde broadcasted as part of TV5Monde Secrets d'Histoire series in 2014 - French narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/b/b4/La-Grande-Duchesse-Charlotte-de-Luxembourg-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Icon and mother of her country, heroine of the resistance and symbol of 175 years of independence, Charlotte of Luxembourg was one of the major European monarchs of the twentieth century.
